{"tid":1684930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(轉載) 內地新興財路 狐狸精培訓班大戰太太改造課程","createTime":"2019-10-31T10:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T11:20:09.000Z","uid":121213,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fb01c4f6ae6a84bc54a6dcced654c42e7e60b5ad","tid":1684930,"uid":121213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_xSB9WVH9kXaVEL87Y9mjw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTUwO2g9Mjgz/https://media.zenfs.com/en/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/f5d738aed934630c8d67b30970bb07d1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F_xSB9WVH9kXaVEL87Y9mjw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTUwO2g9Mjgz%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2Ff5d738aed934630c8d67b30970bb07d1&h=6116c16a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇到澳門大亨最終都係同元配一齊，第三者敗走但係拎到億億聲分手費，<br />\n難怪會有人開班教人做狐狸精！<br />\n內地真係有咁嘅培訓班，幾萬蚊學費加幾日密集式訓練，<br />\n保證釣到金龜，甚至如果畢業後冇著落的話，介紹埋你識有錢人咁話。<br />\n咁大婆可以點？之前有套網路故事講「情敵勸退師」，<br />\n而家市面上真係有咁樣嘅專家，同狐狸精進行調解。<br />\n除此之外，與其日防夜防，不如做好自己，等老公唔出去搵食，<br />\n所以又衍生另一種課程︰名媛培訓班！<br />\n教嘅包括馬術、插花呢啲提升品味嘅高級玩意，<br />\n仲有情感溝通技巧、廚藝呢啲「軟功」底子，就連&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n「房中術」都有教。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B0%E8%88%88%E8%B2%A1%E8%B7%AF-%E7%8B%90%E7%8B%B8%E7%B2%BE%E5%9F%B9%E8%A8%93%E7%8F%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B0%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%AA%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%E8%AA%B2%E7%A8%8B-065253723.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2588%2588%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E7%258B%2590%25E7%258B%25B8%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E5%259F%25B9%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%258F%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%2580%25A0%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E7%25A8%258B-065253723.html&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA426uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=c22dce14\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B0